        "translation": "<span class='transliteration'>[pArtha]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092a\u093e\u0930\u094d\u0925]</span> Arjuna, <span class='transliteration'>[EShA buddhi:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u090f\u0937\u093e \u092c\u0941\u0926\u094d\u0927\u093f\u0903]</span> this learning <span class='transliteration'>[sAnkhyE]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0938\u093e\u0919\u094d\u0916\u094d\u092f\u0947]</span> about the knowledge of the Self <span class='transliteration'>[abhihitA]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0905\u092d\u093f\u0939\u093f\u0924\u093e]</span> has been given <span class='transliteration'>[tE]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0924\u0947]</span> to you. <span class='transliteration'>[yayA buddhyA yukta:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092f\u092f\u093e \u092c\u0941\u0926\u094d\u0927\u094d\u092f\u093e \u092f\u0941\u0915\u094d\u0924\u0903]</span> With this knowledge <span class='transliteration'>[karmabandham prahAsyasi]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0915\u0930\u094d\u092e\u092c\u0928\u094d\u0927\u092e\u094d \u092a\u094d\u0930\u0939\u093e\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0938\u093f]</span> you will overthrow your bonds, which are imposed by your past actions. <span class='transliteration'>[shr`Nu]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0936\u0943\u0923\u0941]</span> Listen <span class='transliteration'>[imAm]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0907\u092e\u093e\u092e\u094d]</span> to this teaching <span class='transliteration'>[yOgE]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092f\u094b\u0917\u0947]</span> in the form of actions that are done for the purpose of attaining moksha.",
