        "translation": "<span class='transliteration'>[yOga mAyA samAvr'ta:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092f\u094b\u0917 \u092e\u093e\u092f\u093e \u0938\u092e\u093e\u0935\u0943\u0924\u0903]</span> Being covered by My miraculous association with a human form, <span class='transliteration'>[nAham prakAsha:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0928\u093e\u0939\u092e\u094d \u092a\u094d\u0930\u0915\u093e\u0936\u0903]</span> I am not apparent in My brilliance <span class='transliteration'>[sarvasya]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0938\u0930\u094d\u0935\u0938\u094d\u092f]</span> to everyone. <span class='transliteration'>[ayam lOka:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0905\u092f\u092e\u094d \u0932\u094b\u0915\u0903]</span> People of this world, <span class='transliteration'>[mUDha:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092e\u0942\u0922\u0903]</span> being unaware, <span class='transliteration'>[nAbhijAnAti mAm]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0928\u093e\u092d\u093f\u091c\u093e\u0928\u093e\u0924\u093f \u092e\u093e\u092e\u094d]</span> do not know Me <span class='transliteration'>[ajam]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0905\u091c\u092e\u094d]</span> as the one who is without birth, <span class='transliteration'>[avyayam]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0905\u0935\u094d\u092f\u092f\u092e\u094d]</span> who does not diminish in any way.",
