        "shloka": "anEka bAhUdara vaktra nEtrampashyAmi tvAm sarvata: ananta rUpam |<br>nAntam na madhyam na puna: tavA_dimpashyAmi vishvEshvara vishvarUpam || 16 ||",
        "translation": "<span class='transliteration'>[anEka]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0905\u0928\u0947\u0915]</span> The many <span class='transliteration'>[bAhu]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092c\u093e\u0939\u0941]</span> arms, <span class='transliteration'>[udara]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0909\u0926\u0930]</span> torsos, <span class='transliteration'>[vaktra]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0935\u0915\u094d\u0924\u094d\u0930]</span> faces <span class='transliteration'>[nEtram]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0928\u0947\u0924\u094d\u0930\u092e\u094d]</span> and eyes - <span class='transliteration'>[pashyAmi tvam]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092a\u0936\u094d\u092f\u093e\u092e\u093f \u0924\u094d\u0935\u092e\u094d]</span> I see you <span class='transliteration'>[ananta rUpam]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0905\u0928\u0928\u094d\u0924 \u0930\u0942\u092a\u092e\u094d]</span> in Your endless form <span class='transliteration'>[sarvata:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0938\u0930\u094d\u0935\u0924\u0903]</span> in every way. <span class='transliteration'>[vishvEshvara]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0935\u093f\u0936\u094d\u0935\u0947\u0936\u094d\u0935\u0930]</span> O Lord of the universe, <span class='transliteration'>[vishvarUpa]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0935\u093f\u0936\u094d\u0935\u0930\u0942\u092a]</span> You have the universe as Your body. <span class='transliteration'>[na antam pashyAmi]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0928 \u0905\u0928\u094d\u0924\u092e\u094d \u092a\u0936\u094d\u092f\u093e\u092e\u093f]</span> I do not see its end, <span class='transliteration'>[Adim na]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0906\u0926\u093f\u092e\u094d \u0928]</span> I do not see its beginning <span class='transliteration'>[puna: madhyam na]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092a\u0941\u0928\u0903 \u092e\u0927\u094d\u092f\u092e\u094d \u0928]</span> and I don't see a mid-point. ",
