        "shloka": "lElihyasE grasamAna: samantAtlOkAn samagrAn vadanai: jvaladbhi: |<br>tEjObhi: ApUrya jagat samagrambhAsa: tavOgrA: pratapanti viShNO || 30 ||",
        "translation": "<span class='transliteration'>[viShNO]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0935\u093f\u0937\u094d\u0923\u094b]</span> Vishnu, <span class='transliteration'>[lElihyasE]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0932\u0947\u0932\u093f\u0939\u094d\u092f\u0938\u0947]</span> You are licking Your lips, <span class='transliteration'>[grAsamAna:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0917\u094d\u0930\u093e\u0938\u092e\u093e\u0928\u0903]</span> swallowing <span class='transliteration'>[lOkAn samagrAn]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0932\u094b\u0915\u093e\u0928\u094d \u0938\u092e\u0917\u094d\u0930\u093e\u0928\u094d]</span> all these people <span class='transliteration'>[samantAt]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0938\u092e\u0928\u094d\u0924\u093e\u0924\u094d]</span> entirely <span class='transliteration'>[jvaladbhi: vadanai:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u091c\u094d\u0935\u0932\u0926\u094d\u092d\u093f\u0903 \u0935\u0926\u0928\u0948\u0903]</span> with your flaming mouth. <span class='transliteration'>[tava ugrA: bhAsA:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0924\u0935 \u0909\u0917\u094d\u0930\u093e\u0903 \u092d\u093e\u0938\u093e\u0903]</span> Your terrific brilliance <span class='transliteration'>[ApUrya]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0906\u092a\u0942\u0930\u094d\u092f]</span> fills <span class='transliteration'>[jagat samagram]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u091c\u0917\u0924\u094d \u0938\u092e\u0917\u094d\u0930\u092e\u094d]</span> the whole universe <span class='transliteration'>[tEjObhi:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0924\u0947\u091c\u094b\u092d\u093f\u0903]</span> with various energies <span class='transliteration'>[pratapanti]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092a\u094d\u0930\u0924\u092a\u0928\u094d\u0924\u093f]</span> and they burn.",
