        "shloka": "sanjaya uvAcha -<br>EtachChr'tvA vachanam kEshavasyakr'tAnjali: vEpamAna: kirITI |<br>namaskr'tvA bhUya EvAha kr'ShNamsagadgadam bhIta bhIta: praNamya || 35 ||",
        "translation": "<span class='transliteration'>[sanjaya uvAcha]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0938\u0928\u094d\u091c\u092f \u0909\u0935\u093e\u091a]</span> Sanjaya said - <span class='transliteration'>[Etat shr'tvA]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u090f\u0924\u0924\u094d \u0936\u0943\u0924\u094d\u0935\u093e]</span> Listening to these <span class='transliteration'>[vachanam]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0935\u091a\u0928\u092e\u094d]</span> words <span class='transliteration'>[kEshavasya]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0915\u0947\u0936\u0935\u0938\u094d\u092f]</span> of the Lord, <span class='transliteration'>[kirITI]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0915\u093f\u0930\u0940\u091f\u0940]</span> Arjuna <span class='transliteration'>[namaskr'tvA]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0928\u092e\u0938\u094d\u0915\u0943\u0924\u094d\u0935\u093e]</span> performed salutations <span class='transliteration'>[vEpamAna:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0935\u0947\u092a\u092e\u093e\u0928\u0903]</span> while trembling <span class='transliteration'>[kr'tAnjali:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0915\u0943\u0924\u093e\u0928\u094d\u091c\u0932\u093f\u0903]</span> with folded hands <span class='transliteration'>[bhUya Eva]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092d\u0942\u092f \u090f\u0935]</span> and once again <span class='transliteration'>[Aha kr'ShNam]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0906\u0939 \u0915\u0943\u0937\u094d\u0923\u092e\u094d]</span> spoke to Krishna <span class='transliteration'>[bhIta bhIta:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092d\u0940\u0924 \u092d\u0940\u0924\u0903]</span> with great fear, <span class='transliteration'>[sagadgadam]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0938\u0917\u0926\u094d\u0917\u0926\u092e\u094d]</span> with a voice choked with emotion, <span class='transliteration'>[praNamya]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092a\u094d\u0930\u0923\u092e\u094d\u092f]</span> with a bowed head.",
