        "translation": "<span class='transliteration'>[asau shatru:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0905\u0938\u094c \u0936\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0941\u0903]</span> 'This enemy <span class='transliteration'>[mayA hata:]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u092e\u092f\u093e \u0939\u0924\u0903]</span> is killed by me. <span class='transliteration'>[haniShyE]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0939\u0928\u093f\u0937\u094d\u092f\u0947]</span> I will kill <span class='transliteration'>[aparAn]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0905\u092a\u0930\u093e\u0928\u094d]</span> others <span class='transliteration'>[api]</span><span class='sanskrit'>[\u0905\u092a\u093f]</span> too'.",
